            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "But that actually makes this push for bipartisanship worse — he understands the crisis, and yet his reflex is to first and foremost try to appease the GOP. No matter what Republican lawmakers do, Biden is ",
